:154,"path":155,"stem":156},"全文搜索","/docs/advanced/fulltext-search","docs/7.advanced/1.fulltext-search",{"title":158,"path":159,"stem":160},"原始内容","/docs/advanced/raw-content","docs/7.advanced/2.raw-content",{"title":162,"path":163,"stem":164},"SQL 存储","/docs/advanced/database","docs/7.advanced/3.database",{"title":166,"path":167,"stem":168},"调试工具","/docs/advanced/tools","docs/7.advanced/4.tools",{"title":170,"path":171,"stem":172},"钩子","/docs/advanced/hooks","docs/7.advanced/5.hooks",{"title":174,"path":175,"stem":176},"自定义来源","/docs/advanced/custom-source","docs/7.advanced/6.custom-source",{"title":178,"path":179,"stem":180},"LLM 集成","/docs/advanced/llms","docs/7.advanced/7.llms",{"title":182,"path":183,"stem":184},"转换器","/docs/advanced/transformers","docs/7.advanced/8.transformers",{"title":186,"icon":187,"path":188,"stem":189,"children":190,"page":42},"Nuxt Studio","i-lucide-monitor","/docs/studio","docs/8.studio",[191,195,199,203,207,211],{"title":192,"path":193,"stem":194},"设置","/docs/studio/setup","docs/8.studio/1.setup",{"title":196,"path":197,"stem":198},"同步","/docs/studio/github","docs/8.studio/2.github",{"title":200,"path":201,"stem":202},"内容编辑器","/docs/studio/content","docs/8.studio/3.content",{"title":204,"path":205,"stem":206},"媒体库","/docs/studio/medias","docs/8.studio/4.medias",{"title":208,"path":209,"stem":210},"应用配置","/docs/studio/config","docs/8.studio/5.config",{"title":212,"path":213,"stem":214},"本地调试","/docs/studio/debug","docs/8.studio/6.debug",{"page":216,"surround":407},{"id":217,"title":218,"body":219,"description":400,"extension":401,"links":402,"meta":403,"navigation":404,"path":197,"seo":405,"stem":198,"__hash__":406},"docs/docs/8.studio/2.github.md","Studio 与 GitHub 之间的实时同步",{"type":220,"value":221,"toc":389},"minimark",[222,229,233,250,252,261,270,274,277,321,336,352,355,363,370,373,376],[223,224,225],"tip",{},[226,227,228],"p",{},"本节解释了 Studio 与 GitHub 之间的同步行为。此过程直接由平台处理，无需任何外部操作。本页面的目的是提供纯粹的信息。",[230,231,232],"h2",{"id":232},"概述",[226,234,235,236,243,244,249],{},"Nuxt Studio 集成了 ",[237,238,242],"a",{"href":239,"rel":240},"https://github.com",[241],"nofollow","GitHub"," API，实现 Studio 与您的 GitHub 仓库之间的顺畅同步。这一顶级集成是通过利用 ",[237,245,248],{"href":246,"rel":247},"https://docs.github.com/en/developers/apps/getting-started-with-apps/about-apps#about-github-apps",[241],"GitHub 应用"," 实现的。",[230,251,12],{"id":12},[226,253,254,255,260],{},"在创建 Studio 项目时，您需要在您的个人账户或您管理的组织中安装 ",[237,256,259],{"href":257,"rel":258},"https://github.com/apps/nuxt-studio",[241],"Nuxt Studio GitHub 应用","。安装 GitHub 应用需要组织所有权或仓库中的管理员权限。如果您没有必要的权限，仓库所有者需要批准该请求。",[226,262,263,264,269],{},"您可以通过点击应用内的任意位置的 ",[237,265,268],{"href":266,"rel":267},"https://github.com/apps/nuxt-studio/installations/new",[241],"使用 GitHub 安装"," 访问安装页面。",[271,272,273],"h3",{"id":273},"权限",[226,275,276],{},"安装我们的 GitHub 应用时，系统会提示您授予某些权限：",[278,279,280,300],"ul",{},[281,282,283,284,288,289,288,292,295,296,299],"li",{},"对 ",[285,286,287],"code",{},"actions","、",[285,290,291],{},"metadata",[285,293,294],{},"members"," 和 ",[285,297,298],{},"plan"," 的读取权限",[281,301,283,302,288,305,288,308,288,311,288,314,295,317,320],{},[285,303,304],{},"secrets",[285,306,307],{},"administration",[285,309,310],{},"contents",[285,312,313],{},"pages",[285,315,316],{},"pull requests",[285,318,319],{},"workflows"," 的读写权限",[226,322,323,324,326,327,329,330,332,333,335],{},"我们需要对 ",[285,325,287],{}," 的读取权限，以便在拉取请求或仓库默认分支的工作流运行失败时发送通知。",[285,328,291],{}," 是必需的，用于获取仓库数据，",[285,331,294],{}," 用于导入您的组织成员和仓库协作者，",[285,334,298],{}," 用于根据您的 GitHub 账户计划推荐功能。",[226,337,338,339,288,341,288,343,288,345,288,347,295,349,351],{},"Nuxt Studio 代表您创建仓库、分支、拉取请求，并执行提交和合并。我们还提供一键部署到 GitHub Pages，支持工作流和环境变量密钥的即时预览和管理。为实现此目的，我们需要对 ",[285,340,307],{},[285,342,310],{},[285,344,313],{},[285,346,316],{},[285,348,319],{},[285,350,304],{}," 的读写权限。",[271,353,354],{"id":354},"仓库安装",[226,356,357,358,362],{},"安装我们的 GitHub 应用时，系统会提示您选择所有仓库或其中的子集。此选择可随时通过访问 ",[237,359,361],{"href":266,"rel":360},[241],"GitHub 应用设置"," 进行更改。",[226,364,365,366,369],{},"点击 ",[285,367,368],{},"Install"," 后，Nuxt Studio 会安装您所选的每个仓库，使您能够执行上述所有操作。",[230,371,372],{"id":372},"卸载",[226,374,375],{},"所有从 GitHub 导入的数据都直接关联到您的 GitHub 应用安装。如果您卸载该 GitHub 应用，所有相关数据将被删除。",[226,377,378,379,383,384,388],{},"如果您删除 GitHub 仓库，关联的 Nuxt Studio 项目也将自动移除。但是，如果该项目订阅了团队计划，订阅不会自动取消。您需要通过 ",[237,380,382],{"href":381},"","Lemon Squeezy"," 手动结束订阅，或",[237,385,387],{"href":386},"team@nuxt.studio","联系我们"," 寻求帮助。",{"title":381,"searchDepth":390,"depth":390,"links":391},4,[392,394,399],{"id":232,"depth":393,"text":232},2,{"id":12,"depth":393,"text":12,"children":395},[396,398],{"id":273,"depth":397,"text":273},3,{"id":354,"depth":397,"text":354},{"id":372,"depth":393,"text":372},"Nuxt Studio 与 GitHub 原生同步。安装 Nuxt Studio GitHub 应用，并直接从 Studio 启用内容发布到 GitHub。","md",null,{},{"title":196},{"title":218,"description":400},"jOwxS_ahAALAfnzpFq4XQbzm21X0iAtPmlOmMu_FgzA",[408,410],{"title":192,"path":193,"stem":194,"description":409,"children":-1},"Studio 是用于编辑 Nuxt Content 网站的直观 CMS 界面。编辑你的 Markdown、YAML 和 JSON 文件，并将更改发布到 GitHub。",{"title":200,"path":201,"stem":202,"description":411,"children":-1},"发现并选择您喜欢的内容管理方式，视觉编辑器或代码编辑器。",{"data":413,"body":414},{},{"type":415,"children":416},"root",[417],{"type":418,"tag":226,"props":419,"children":420},"element",{},[421],{"type":422,"value":400},"text",1749797813872]